long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The Select Chrome Extensions notifies Select Members anytime they're on a benefits partner website and directs them to our applicable Member benefit for that brand.

The member will then be able to easily navigate to the benefit redemption page to redeem their exclusive benefit.
